052,644", "bbox": [994.2, 619.7, 1094.2, 640.5]}, {"text": "Casino revenue increased 1% in 2015 compared to 2014 due to a 2% increase in slots revenue as a result of", "bbox": [185.5, 678.0, 1094.2, 698.9]}, {"text": "a 3% increase in slots volume. Table games revenue in 2015 decreased 1% compared to 2014 due to a decrease", "bbox": [143.8, 703.0, 1094.0, 723.9]}, {"text": "in table games volume of 1% and a decrease in tables games hold percentage to 20.5% in 2015 from 20.9% in", "bbox": [143.8, 728.0, 1094.2, 748.9]}, {"text": "2014.", "bbox": [143.8, 753.0, 190.7, 773.9]}, {"text": "Casino revenue in 2014 increased 1% compared to 2013 as a result of a 4% increase in table games revenue", "bbox": [185.5, 798.9, 1094.1, 819.7]}, {"text": "compared to 2013 due to an increase in table games volume of 2% and an increase in tables games hold", "bbox": [143.8, 823.9, 1094.2, 844.7]}, {"text": "percentage to 20.9% in 2014 from 20.5% in 2013. Slots revenue increased slightly compared to 2013.", "bbox": [143.8, 848.9, 993.1, 869.7]}, {"text": "Rooms revenue increased 6% in 2015 compared to 2014 as a result of a 7% increase in REVPAR at our Las", "bbox": [185.5, 894.8, 1094.2, 915.6]}, {"text": "Vegas Strip resorts. Rooms revenue increased 7% in 2014 compared to 2013 as a result of an 8% increase in", "bbox": [143.8, 919.8, 1094.2, 940.6]}, {"text": "REVPAR at our Las Vegas Strip resorts. The following table shows key hotel statistics for our Las Vegas Strip", "bbox": [143.8, 944.8, 1094.1, 965.6]}, {"text": "resorts:", "bbox": [143.8, 969.8, 205.2, 990.6]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [764.7, 1011.5, 998.5, 1032.4]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [710.7, 1040.7, 752.4, 1061.6]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [860.8, 1040.7, 902.4, 1061.6]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [1010.8, 1040.7, 1052.5, 1061.6]}, {"text": "Occupancy .......................................................", "bbox": [143.8, 1074.0, 644.0, 1094.8]}, {"text": "93%", "bbox": [755.8, 1074.0, 794.0, 1094.